{"type":"step-attempt","step":"cross-boundary-invariants","sessionId":"e4811531-d917-4af3-b731-4a5c0412a0f9","outcome":{"verdict":"approved","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/verdict-fidelity-and-fixer-noop/cross-boundary-invariants-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"approved":false,"findings":[{"severity":"medium","resolution":"fixable","file":"src/core/step/executor.ts","title":"verdictOverride silently overrides producer `status:error` — explicit failure signal suppressed","rationale":"The verdictOverride application at L853-855 is unconditional. When code-fixer completes with completionReason=success but calls report_result({status:'error'}) (explicit failure), and noOpDetect fires (no source files changed), verdictOverride='needs-fix' overrides verdict='error'. design.md D3 states 'approved を上書き' but the implementation overrides any verdict including 'error'. This breaks the implicit invariant that a producer step's explicit status:error signal results in 'error' routing. The pipeline loops to exhaustion instead of escalating.","line":853}],"observations":[{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/step/executor.ts","title":"verifyFindingRefs skips LOW/MEDIUM fixable findings from regression-gate","rationale":"collectVerdictAffectingFindings filters critical|high|decision-needed only. deriveRegressionGateVerdict now returns needs-fix for medium/low fixable findings, but those bypass verifyFindingRefs ref-validation. Risk is mitigated: regression-gate ledger contains already-validated findings from prior reviewer runs.","line":808},{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/step/code-fixer.ts","title":"isFixerContinuation returns true after a no-op — continuation prompt sent to an agent that did nothing","rationale":"After a no-op needs-fix result, state.steps['code-fixer'] has a run entry. The next iteration's isFixerContinuation returns true and sends a short continuation prompt, despite no meaningful prior context. Bounded by exhaustion guard; non-blocking."}]},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-07-03T13:39:08.147Z","endedAt":"2026-07-03T13:45:08.450Z"}
